OL,3,CUK must plan for Iran war to continue
OL,4,C'for some time', warns Starmer
OL,6,FBritain must be prepared for the war
OL,7,Fin Iran to continue "for some time",
OL,8,Fthe prime minister has warned MPs.
OL,10,FSpeaking before the liaison committee
OL,11,Fon Monday, Sir Keir Starmer warned the
OL,12,Fcountry must not fall into the "false
OL,13,Fcomfort" of thinking there would be "a
OL,14,Fquick and early end" to the war.
OL,16,F"I think all our focus and energy has
OL,17,Fto be in the swift de-escalation, but
OL,18,Fwe've got to plan on the basis that it
OL,19,Fcould go on for some time, and that's
OL,20,Fthe way in which we'll plan this
OL,21,Fafternoon," he told MPs.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
