OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774314171
OL,3,CUK must plan for Iran war to continue
OL,4,C'for some time', warns Starmer
OL,6,F"Since the conflict started, I've been
OL,7,Freally clear with the team that we
OL,8,Fmustn't fall into the sort of false
OL,9,Fcomfort of thinking that there will
OL,10,Fnecessarily be a quick and early end
OL,11,Fto this.
OL,13,F"We have to plan on the basis there
OL,14,Fmay not be."
OL,16,FThe prime minister was speaking ahead
OL,17,Fof a meeting of the Government's
OL,18,Femergency Cobra committee to discuss
OL,19,Fhow to handle the economic impact of
OL,20,Fthe conflict.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@LO]
