OL,3,CUK must plan for Iran war to continue
OL,4,C'for some time', warns Starmer
OL,6,FHis words come after his US
OL,7,Fcounterpart Donald Trump signalled a
OL,8,Fdegree of de-escalation in the
OL,9,Fconflict, posting on Truth Social that
OL,10,Ftalks between the US and Iran had been
OL,11,F"very good and productive
OL,12,Fconversations".
OL,14,FStarmer said the UK was aware these
OL,15,Ftalks were taking place, and
OL,16,Freiterated his view that we must "de-
OL,17,Fescalate and bring an end to this
OL,18,Fconflict as swiftly as possible."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
