FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774314171
OL,3,CUK must plan for Iran war to continue
OL,4,C'for some time', warns Starmer
OL,6,FThere were also suggestions from MPs
OL,7,Fthat the UK may face supply shortages,
OL,8,Fdue to the closure of the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz and a dwindling global oil
OL,10,Fsupply.
OL,12,FAddressing this, the prime minister
OL,13,Fsaid: "I can reassure the committee
OL,14,Fthat we haven't any meaningful concern
OL,15,Fabout energy supplies."
OL,17,FDefence Secretary John Healey
OL,18,Fconfirmed British ship HMS Dragon
OL,19,Fwould begin operating in the region on
OL,20,FMonday night.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
