OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774314171
OL,3,CUK must plan for Iran war to continue
OL,4,C'for some time', warns Starmer
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Defence Secretary John
OL,7,FHealey confirmed British ship HMS
OL,8,FDragon had arrived in the region and
OL,9,Fwould begin operations on Monday night.
OL,11,F"Tonight, (it) begins operational
OL,12,Fintegration into Cyprus's defence,
OL,13,Falongside allies," Healey told MPs
OL,14,Fwhile speaking in the house of commons.
OL,16,FAddressing the news that two missiles
OL,17,Fwere fired towards the British-US
OL,18,Fmilitary base Diego Garcia, Healey
OL,19,Fsaid the government had been "blunt"
OL,20,Fand "open" with the public.
OL,26,@sD@KpmsD@Npn
