OL,3,CUK must plan for Iran war to continue
OL,4,C'for some time', warns Starmer
OL,6,F"There is no assessment that we are
OL,7,Fbeing targeted in the UK in that way,"
OL,8,FHealey added.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FUnusually, the Governor of the Bank of
OL,16,FEngland Andrew Bailey will also join
OL,17,Fthe Cobra meeting later on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
