OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774314171
OL,3,CUK must plan for Iran war to continue
OL,4,C'for some time', warns Starmer
OL,6,FThe public has already seen everyday
OL,7,Fprices for things like petrol and
OL,8,Fmortgages rise in response to Iran's
OL,9,Feffective closure of the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz.
OL,12,FSpeaking to the liaison committee
OL,13,Fahead of this meeting, the prime
OL,14,Fminister confirmed his cabinet would
OL,15,Fdiscuss what measures could be
OL,16,Fimplemented to help ease these rising
OL,17,Fcosts for the public.
OL,19,F"This afternoon we will be looking at
OL,20,Fa wider set of measures," said Starmer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
